text:
Aaishi yaar kya likhu ab mai tere baare mein. Chalo purani baate yaad karte hai. Pehli baar tu mila tha 3-top pe tab mujhe yaad hai tu jo bolta tha bohot logo ko samaz nahi aata tha par mujhe aata tha. Tujhe dekh kar hi laga ki yaar ye aadmi apna aaacha dost ban sakta hai. Baate karte rahe tab ek din dhoni related fact share kiya tune wing wale group pe tab pata chala ki tu dhoni fan hai tab toh saare taar jud gaye aur kya hi chahiye tha firğŸ˜‚. Mujhe yaad hai usi din class k bahar mila aur maine tujhe pucha tha tu bhi dhoni fan hai aur tune bola haan fir apan mast baate karte karte hall gye the Sath mein CSK ki matches dekhte the wo toh nhi bhulunge kabhi. Fir toh sabse accha time aaya apna sath mein jab galaxy mein dance karne k liye gye. pehle din se mujhe yaad hai har chiz mein sath rehte the... streching ,warm-up, running sab mein sath me rehte the. sath mein sikhe sab. yaad hai wo pehla din jab bohot dance kar liye fir chalna mushkil ho gya tha stairs chadne mein kya haalat ho rhi thi. fir jab galaxy jeete tab kitne maze kiye sath mein uske baad aur achhe dost ban gye apan. But sadly every good time has an end. Apne raaste alag ho gye q ki tu gaya SAE mein aur mai reh gya dance mein. Mujhe hamesha lagta tha dance karte waqt ki mai akela hu koi sath nhi(jab tak sashwat nhi aaya lekin wo bhi saala late aaya kaafi). Mujhe bhi le jaata yaar SAEğŸ˜¥ğŸ˜¥ sath mein kaam karte. Fir toh 2 saal milna kam ho gya kaafi bas wing mein kabhi kabhi milte theğŸ˜­ğŸ˜­. Fir abhi time mila hai sath mein jab dono dual kar rhe. Aur abhi jo hamne time bitaya 2 mahine sath mein wo bhi best time tha. But not to forget ye end toh nhi hi hai apne pass aur time hai sath mein aur memories banayenge. Abhi jab bhi milenge bohot maze karenge. And as promised mai pakka maal fukunga jab acchi job lag jayegi. aur haan ek baat bolunga shayad  buri lag sakti hai tujhe but bura mat manna...tu kabhi kabhi bhool jaata hai ki mai dil pe leleta hu baat toh kabhi kabhi mujhe baat hurt karti hai teri.. jaise aakhri din wo avinash k sath baithe the aur tu mazaak kar rha tha(bhai behen wagera kch bol rha tha) but chill hai wo matter nhi karta mai bhool bhi jaata hu jaldiğŸ˜‚ .Main baat na bhool jaau bc.... achhi baate(gyan) batata haina meko sunne mein bohot accha lagta hai. 
Thanks man to be part of my life. I hope ki college k baad bhi apan pass hi rhe...contact mein rhe.(sath mein gym kareğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚)
author: Parag Nandaram Sonkusare

text:
Avinash yaar, bohot kam log hote hai jo jeeven me apne wo impact daalte hai IITK ki journey mein aise bohot kam log the , aur mai kaafi garv se keh sakta hu tu unme se ek hai. Apne 4 saal bhi kya badhiya the, haan bhale hi aakhri saal ne thodi maa chuda li. Sahi kaha tune jo trio bana tha apna wo best tha. Kitni maa chudayi yaar wo baat baat pe Z square ghumne jaana, pizza hut mein mobile repair karne dena. 1st year mein maine  tujhe pehli baar notice kiya jab aaishi ko milne aata tha. Aisi hi dosti chalu hui thi. Haage k usspaar wale waise hi bohot kam aate theğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚. Lekin tu kaafi interesting aadmi laga tha meko. Fir toh normal dosti maintained thi ..lekin asli maza toh wahi aaya trip pe. Maze  kya hote hai maine bhi wahi jaana. Ghar se door dosto ka sath. Pata hai ki kahi bhi gaand fati bas dost hi hai aage piche bachane wale aur tab hi doston ki asli value pata chalti hai. Aur tabhi saaro k sath dosti gehri ho gyi. Trekking k maze toh kabhi nahi bhulunga. Complete trip kya hoti hai wo tab pata chala. Sath mein aur maze karte yaar lekinâ€¦â€¦â€¦â€¦.. Kash tera dual ho jaatağŸ˜­ğŸ˜­.
Dual hota toh aur kitne maze hote, chick blast hotağŸ˜¥. Khair abhi jo nhi ho sakta uske yaad nhi karte.   Chick blast se yaad aaya tum aur ankit chick blast ko toh bhool hi gye. Chick blast mein bhi toh kitni maa chudayiâ€¦ jab bhi kisi ka mann nhi lag rha, mess mein khane ka mann nhi hai.. To chalo chick blastğŸ˜‚.
Trip toh apni ek aur hui thi jo lagta hai sab bhool gye likhna. BLUE WORLD water park wali. Usme bhi kitne maze aaye the bhaiii. Garmi mein apan sab chale gye aur kya toh maze kiye the . water slides mein saurav ka chehra toh kabhi nhi bhulungağŸ¤£ğŸ¤£.
Ab baat karte hai aakhri do mahine ki. Sabse pehle toh management k upar muto bhenchod jisne ye socha ki dual wale ek hall mein rahenge aur baaki saare dure hall mein. Soch yaar kitne maze hote agar ek hall mein rehte ...lekin saalo ne maa chudali. Kaafi kch reh gya yaar. Apni dosti ka burger ki tarah ho gyi starting mein aur ending mein bhalehi sukhi reh gyi lekin bich mein bohot juicy thiğŸ¤£ğŸ¤£. 
Yahi kahunga aakhri mein ki kaafi galtiya bhi ki hai maine(anjane mein) uske liye maaf karna. Kabhi bhula toh nhi payenge tum ko ho sake toh hame bhi yaad rakhna. Milte hai kabhi kisi duniya k kone mein... tab tak in yaado ko sambhal k rakhna.
P.S -- BHai BHAiiii  kya maze aaye the dance karne main pari k sathğŸ˜ğŸ˜ğŸ˜.
author: Parag Nandaram Sonkusare

text:
yaar pizza hut ki baat karke k tune toh haseen kaade taaza kardi. Kya din the wo bhi. Memoirs me mai sabke apne 4 saal ki journey revist kar rha hu. apni journey bhi uniquw thi. last me thoda bura time tha lekin lets not ruin the speical moments we had just bcoz of that lil bump. toh revisit start karte hai:
yaad hai mujhe tu pehli baar kaise mila tha . Tu aur IP(ğŸ) aaye the room tab pehli baar mila tujhe aur tu aate hi gaaliyo me baate karne laga tab maine socha ki ye kaise log hai kaise baat karte haiğŸ˜‚. Lekin ab sochta hu ki normal hi toh tha ğŸ¤£ğŸ¤£.  apan tab itni acchese nhi jaante the pehle pehle. fir apan ne ek sath dance kiya freshers mein. asli dosti hui jab 2nd year start hua. tab tere room mein aana janaa start hua aur tab soni bhi rehta tha room mein tum dono ki harkate dekhne mein maza aati thi meko. fir tu akela rehne laga . tab tere room mein aata tha tab tu sota rehta tha ur mere aate hi darr k uth jaaata tha aur fir bolta tha aree yaar mujhe padhna tha lekin mai so gya mera kya hoga...ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚. tu hamesha se mehnati tha shayad aaj mai itna mehnat karta hu toh kaafi kch tere se sikha hu. asli maze tab aane start hue jab avinash tu aur mai milke chize karne start kar diye. sath mein kitni bakchodi karte the ghumne jaate the, pizza hut wali trips hamesha yaad rahegi.  ek baar yaad hai apan tino ghum rhe the tab meri cycle ka break kaam nhi kar rha tha .. tab maine bola sidha jaana hai aur tu mud gya aur fir tere wajah se mai bhi mud gya fir tum dono sidhe gye aur mai ad gya kone mein fir wapas aaya tab dono hass rhe the  dhire dhire. tab maine kaha tha bol kaunsi gaali du tujheğŸ¤£ğŸ¤£. fir tere birthday k din bahar movie dekhne jaane wale the tab aadhe raste se tu aero club leke gya tab kitne gaali diye tujhe humne milkeğŸ¤£ğŸ¤£ aur tere 3rd year wale bday pe sabne kitne maze kiye the. lekin sab bacho meri lene lage the. OAT pe baithke kya maze kiye the. Mirzapur dekhe sath mein jaha patli patli sadke thiğŸ¤£ğŸ¤£. sath mein padhe (Ghanta padheğŸ¤£ğŸ¤£). tere sath trip reh gyi lekin chinta nhi hai meri job lagegi aur tu tab tak IAS bhi ban jayega fir foriegn trip karenge.
  kaafi maze kiye yaar sath mein. bas wo last wala time agar erase ho jaaye toh kitna mast. wo bhi isiliye hua q ki apne halls alag ho gye the.  wo jo bhi ho tere sath bitaye hue pal special rahenge hamesha aur mai hamesha yaad karunga. tu toh yaad karega hi jab tu ("ba" ko "va" pronounce karega). mai hamesha yaad  karke hasunga ye saare moments(aur last me thoda sa shayad ro bhi dungağŸ¥ºğŸ¥º).

text: Yaaar  IP rulayega kya yaar...itni sweet baate likhdi tune mai kya hi likhu ab. best aadmi tha yaar tu. Apne memories bhale hi kam ho lekin jo thi best thi. galaxy mein kya maze kiye the yaar. usme tere sath sabse special memory hai dance drama wali yaad hai. apan sath mein hi the usme. mai daarr rha tha ki mai bhool jaunga aur tu samjha rha tha mujhe ki nhi sab sahi ho jayega.  fir jab jeet gye kitne maze kiye yaar.ğŸ˜chalo jeetne k toh maze the hi lekin usse zyada maze the jab harr roz chudte the dance karke aur fir sath mein baithte the parathe khane ya canteen meinğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚. mirzapur mein patli sadke dekhiğŸ¤£ğŸ¤£..bahar ghumne gye ..kitne maze kiye bas aakhri 2 mahine mein tu aata toh aur memories bante. tu aaya hi nhiğŸ¥ºğŸ¥º . chalo agli baar pakka milte hai. Until next time!!.

text:
Baat toh sahi kahi tune (mere memoir mein) abhi toh ek saal aur hai toh senti chize toh 1 saal baad wale memoir mein likhunga. Aur main baat coding itni karni hai pancho ki companiyo ki line lag jaaye 20 lakhs k upar wali job hi leni haiğŸ˜‹.

text:
Tushar  yaar mere bhai, waise toh ek saal baad ek hi jagah job karne wale hai ğŸ˜ğŸ˜ , chalo fir bhi purani baate yaad karte hai. Aisa koi time yaad karna mushkil hai jo IITK mein tere sath na ho(specially teri brach change k baad se) bancho harr class sath mein jaate, labs khana khane, gym, maa chudane harr chiz toh sath mein hi kii hai. Ab tere ko toh btaya hi tha maine ki kitna kch sikha hai maine tujhse tere hi dikhaye nakshe kadam par chal rha hu abhi bhiğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚. 
Pehle se start karte hai:
Tu mujhe pehle mila tha jab mai aur anshul pehli baar apni 3top wali room pe aaye the aur tu soya tha. Mai samaan leke aaya â€¦ tu tab bhi soya tha...mai aur kch zaruri kaam karke aaya fir tu soya thağŸ¤£ğŸ¤£. Fir uth gya aur fir pehli baar baat ki apnanne. 
Pehle pehle kitna ladte the aur aaj dekh ..kitna change ho gye haiğŸ˜‚. Kitni bakchodi karte the yaar apan sab..baarish aayi toh chalo baarish mein cycling karne chale gye ..toofaan aaya ya bohot thandi ho rhi hai toh terrace pe bakchodi...terrace pe sona(sabki pics hai waise ğŸ˜‚)
Pics se yaad aaya bhai wo jo tere kaarnamo ki videos hai uska kya karna hai(3top pe daalduğŸ˜)?  Wo BB ki videos sath mein dekhte the, aur movies projector pe dekhte the. Wo Z square jaake chicken pelna. Chicken se yaad aayaa abe tu hi toh tha jisne chicken khana sikhayağŸ˜‚. Fir trip pe gye â€¦.yaar trip kya awesome chiz thi. Mai toh kahunga sabse awesome chiz trip hi thi.  Sabse excited tu hi tha. Yaar ek aur karwa de. Yaar waise ye saari choti choti baate itni saari hui hai ki kya kya likhu photos dekhta hu toh saare yaade taaza ho jaate hai aur likhne lagunga toh raat ho jayegiğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚. 
Ab baat karte hai last 2 mahino ki...yaar kitne maze kiye tum teeno k sath. Sabse badhiya baat hui ki tu hall 12 mein rehne aaya. Haan lekin iss baat ka regret hamesha rahega ki hamesha tumhare sath nhi reh paaya ...tum tino ne mere bina bhi kaafi maze kiya lekin padhna zaruri thana.. tere lab reports kaun banatağŸ˜. But seriously abhi jab yaad karta hu toh lagta hai yaar mujhe kaafi regret hota hai. But jo bhi ho jitne bhi maze kiye sath mein bohot mazaa aaya aur kaash waisa time firse aaye. 
LAst mein yahi kahunga ki yaar bohot impact raha hai tera mere life pe. Maza aaya 4 saal aur aage bhi ayega hi ğŸ˜‰. Yaad karte rehna aur baat waat bhi karte rehnaâ€¦..
 until next timeğŸ˜Š.
